comment:
* Payload for the {@link AttributionSource} class needed to interoperate
 * with different languages.
 * 
 * {@hide}

variables.name: pid
variables.comment: The PID that is accessing the permission protected data.

variables.name: uid
variables.comment: The UID that is accessing the permission protected data.

variables.name: deviceId
variables.comment:
* The default device ID from where the permission protected data is read.
   * @see Context#DEVICE_ID_DEFAULT

variables.name: packageName
variables.comment: The package that is accessing the permission protected data.

variables.name: attributionTag
variables.comment: The attribution tag of the app accessing the permission protected data.

variables.name: renouncedPermissions
variables.comment: Permissions that should be considered revoked regardless if granted.

variables.name: next
variables.comment: support referring to the parcelable as it expects ctor/dtor
